===Pronunciation===
זבוּלן   - זבלוּן -   זבוּלוּן / zebûlûn  zebûlûn  zebûlûn / zeb-oo-loon', zeb-oo-loon', zeb-oo-loon'

===Etymology===
From [[זבל]] {{HH|2082}}; habitation; Zebulon, a son of Jacob; also his territory and tribe

===Proper noun===
'''זבוּלוּן'''

# [[Zebulun]].

